    "content": "## Basic\n\nA toggle button lets folks flip a choice on or off, like switching between two vibes or modes.\n<How toUse=\"buttons/toggle/toggle-demo\" />\n\n## Installation\n<Installation options={{isComponent: true}} items={['toggle']}/>\n\n## Manual Installation\n<Installation options={{isManual: true}} items={['react-aria-components']}/>\n\n<SourceCode toShow={['toggle']}/>\n\n## Appearance\nYou can change the appearance of the toggle button by passing an `appearance` prop.\n<How toUse=\"buttons/toggle/toggle-appearance-demo\" />\n\n## Shape\n\nYou can change the shape of the toggle button by passing a `shape` prop.\n<How toUse=\"buttons/toggle/toggle-shape-demo\" />\n\n## Size\n\nYou can change the size of the toggle button by passing a `size` prop.\n<How toUse=\"buttons/toggle/toggle-size-demo\" />\n\n## Controlled\n\nYou can control the state of the toggle button by passing a `isSelected` prop.\n<How toUse=\"buttons/toggle/toggle-controlled-demo\" />\n\n## Disabled\n\nYou can disable a toggle button by passing a `disabled` prop.\n<How toUse=\"buttons/toggle/toggle-disabled-demo\" />",
