    "content": "## Basic\nVisualize data in a basic radar chart for a simple and effective presentation.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-basic-demo\"/>\n\n## Custom Label\nAdd custom labels to your radar chart to provide additional context and clarity.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-custom-label-demo\"/>\n\n## Dots\nHighlight specific data points in your radar chart using dots for better emphasis.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-dots-demo\"/>\n\n## Grid Circle\nUse a grid circle to organize and display your radar chart data effectively.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-grid-circle-demo\"/>\n\n## Grid Circle Filled\nEnhance your radar chart with filled grid circles for a bolder visual effect.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-grid-circle-filled-demo\"/>\n\n## Grid Circle No Lines\nCreate a minimalist radar chart by removing grid lines and focusing on the data.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-grid-circle-no-lines-demo\"/>\n\n## Grid Custom\nCustomize the grid of your radar chart to align with your specific design requirements.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-grid-custom-demo\"/>\n\n## Grid Filled\nFill the grid of your radar chart to make it visually distinct and engaging.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-grid-filled-demo\"/>\n\n## Grid None\nSimplify your radar chart by removing the grid for a cleaner appearance.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-grid-none-demo\"/>\n\n## Legend\nAdd a legend to your radar chart to improve data interpretation and readability.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-legend-demo\"/>\n\n## Lines Only\nFocus on the lines of your radar chart to emphasize the relationships between data points.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-lines-only-demo\"/>\n\n## Multiple\nVisualize multiple datasets in your radar chart for comparative analysis.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-multiple-demo\"/>\n\n## Radius Axis\nUse a radius axis to better organize and display data in your radar chart.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-radius-axis-demo\"/>\n\n## Icons\nEnhance your radar chart by adding icons for a more engaging and intuitive design.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/radar/radar-chart-icons-demo\"/>",
