    "content": "## Default\nUse the default tooltip settings for a quick and straightforward implementation.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-default-demo\"/>\n\n## Icons\nEnhance your chart tooltips by adding icons for a visually engaging experience.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-icons-demo\"/>\n\n## Custom Label\nCustomize the tooltip labels to better describe the data being presented.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-custom-label-demo\"/>\n\n## Formatter\nFormat tooltip content to present data in a clear and customized way.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-formatter-demo\"/>\n\n## Label Formatter\nAdjust the tooltip label format for improved data clarity and presentation.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-label-formatter-demo\"/>\n\n## Line Indicator\nInclude a line indicator in your tooltips to better highlight relevant data points.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-line-indicator-demo\"/>\n\n## No Indicator\nSimplify tooltips by removing line indicators while keeping focus on the data.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-no-indicator-demo\"/>\n\n## No Label\nCreate minimalistic tooltips by omitting labels and focusing on raw data.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-no-label-demo\"/>\n\n## Advanced\nLeverage advanced tooltip configurations to provide more detailed insights.\n<How withNoPadding={true} isCenter={false} toUse=\"charts/tooltip/tooltip-chart-advance-demo\"/>",
