    "content": "## Basic\nA group of checkboxes that lets you select multiple options at once.\n<How toUse=\"forms/checkbox/checkbox-group-demo\" />\n\n## Installation\n<Installation options={{ isComponent: true }} items={['checkbox']}/>\n\n## Composed Components\n<Composed components={['field']}/>\n\n## Manual Installation\n<Installation options={{ isManual: true }} items={['react-aria-components']}/>\n\n<SourceCode toShow={['checkbox']}/>\n\n## Anatomy\n<Anatomy show='checkbox-group-anatomy'/>\n\n## Description\nAdd a description to the checkbox group using the `description` prop.\n<How minW72 toUse=\"forms/checkbox/checkbox-group-description-demo\" />\n\n## Validation\nThe checkbox group is in an error state.\n<How toUse=\"forms/checkbox/checkbox-group-validation-demo\" />\n\n## Indeterminate\nThe checkbox group is in an indeterminate state.\n<How toUse=\"forms/checkbox/checkbox-group-indeterminate-demo\" />\n\n## Controlled\nControl the checkbox group value with the `value` prop.\n<How minW72 toUse=\"forms/checkbox/checkbox-group-controlled-demo\" />\n\n## Uncontrolled\nControl the checkbox group value with the `defaultValue` prop.\n<How minW72 toUse=\"forms/checkbox/checkbox-group-uncontrolled-demo\" />\n\n## Disabled\nDisable the entire checkbox group by passing the `isDisabled` prop.\n<How minW72 toUse=\"forms/checkbox/checkbox-group-disabled-demo\" />\n\n## Read Only\nWhen you need just a read-only checkbox group, pass the `isReadOnly` prop.\n```\n<CheckboxGroup isReadOnly/>\n```",
